## Reflection Notes

In this task, I created my digital portfolio using GitHub, LinkedIn, and Stack Overflow. 
Each platform serves a different purpose. 
GitHub helps me showcase my coding projects and track my learning progress. 
LinkedIn is useful for building a professional network and presenting my academic background. 
Stack Overflow helps in improving problem-solving skills by allowing users to ask and answer programming-related questions.

This task helped me understand the importance of maintaining a professional online presence. 
Over the next four years, I plan to regularly update my GitHub with projects, stay active on LinkedIn, and use Stack Overflow to learn and solve coding problems. 
These platforms will support my academic growth and future career opportunities.

